{"tid":1497412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家！係好攰好攰好想放棄既時候！仲有好多人支持我地！包括廣州","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:17:28.000Z","uid":135177,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0c2dfafa14683ae712b059212664c496fbaa05","tid":1497412,"uid":135177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"上年香港版食雞未出前<br />\n打大陸版食雞識左班廣州人<br />\n其實佢地都一直話支持我<br />\n上次集會佢都有落黎<br />\n並唔係所有大陸人都係on99咁<br />\n佢地只係唔敢出聲！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信我地香港人一直堅持落去<br />\n總有一日會感染到其他人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星星之火可以燎原<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufXtfhx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufXtfhx.png&h=d882b440&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpiHjKd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpiHjKd.png&h=dd11b1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面呢條link係佢send比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係大陸既義士仲慘.......孤身一人<br />\n所以我地唔可以輸！唔可以放棄<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LJEjhilVddzGdqBnVzoDNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FLJEjhilVddzGdqBnVzoDNA&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=485c2c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LJEjhilVddzGdqBnVzoDNA</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7a2638093844e2b8d5f34e3b845216dee0216fd","tid":1497412,"uid":225818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"大陸人要撐